{"data":[{"id":563757507,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7c90693ab3c4ce27c26ca300e932c302","url_token":"ghj123h","name":"ghj123h","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-418d9205a7034cfe18481716dcd4dbc7_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-418d9205a7034cfe18481716dcd4dbc7_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7c90693ab3c4ce27c26ca300e932c302","user_type":"people","headline":"贴吧@ghj123h：各类话题瞎β回答者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":577,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563757507","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273235,"updated_time":1546346141,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1474,"comment_count":93,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e负质数什么的可以无视它……就权当新提出了一个概念。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e重点来了：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e其逆否命题为：若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是一个质数。\u003cbr\u003e当 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n_0%3D1\" alt=\"n_0=1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 时，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是一个质数。\u003cbr\u003e这是一个真命题，所以该存在命题为真命题。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e在假定-1是质数的情况下否定-1是质数？？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看来这位高中生被自己定义的概念绕晕了，不适合当民科啊（狗头）\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里再认真解释一下吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前面有提到这样的表述：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e设集合 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A\" alt=\"A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e显然“负质数”这个概念是不存在的，因此我们不如严格定义一下：设 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%28%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E-%29%3D%5Cleft%5C%7B2n%7C2n%3Dp_1%2Bp_2%2Cp_1%2Cp_2%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5Ccup%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E-%2Cn%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BZ%7D%5Cright%5C%7D\" alt=\"A(\\mathbb{P}^-)=\\left\\{2n|2n=p_1+p_2,p_1,p_2\\in\\mathbb{P}\\cup\\mathbb{P}^-,n\\in\\mathbb{Z}\\right\\}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，其中 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E-\" alt=\"\\mathbb{P}^-\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 就是所谓的“负质数”集，是一个\u003cb\u003e人为规定\u003c/b\u003e而不是根据性质归纳出的集合。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是质数，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，其中 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为唯一的负质数。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么我们不妨设这样的 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A\" alt=\"A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 叫做 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%28-1%29\" alt=\"A(-1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 。这样，按照上文的思路，可以得到“\u003cb\u003e若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cnotin%7BA%28-1%29%7D\" alt=\"2\\notin{A(-1)}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是一个质数。\u003c/b\u003e”很显然，在这种扩充定义下，我们有 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%28-1%29%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A(-1)}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，所以“-1不是一个质数”不能得到肯定。\u003cb\u003e而且这个结论也是无法得到肯定的：这是因为 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%28-1%29\" alt=\"A(-1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 的定义本身已经蕴含了 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E-\" alt=\"-1\\in\\mathbb{P}^-\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，只要使用到了 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%28-1%29\" alt=\"A(-1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 就必须是质数。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这位高中生之所以搞出了 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，是因为他已经自动\u003cb\u003e把 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 从 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A\" alt=\"A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 的构造条件中扔了出去，也就是他所使用的 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A\" alt=\"A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 和原命题的 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A\" alt=\"A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是一个 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A\" alt=\"A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/b\u003e ，自然而然倒霉的-1也就跟着变成了不是质数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样我们很容易发现这个命题为假： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=8%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"8\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 而 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E-\" alt=\"-1\\in\\mathbb{P}^-\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，事实上这个命题确实是假命题。如果要做的更像一点，可能应该使用特称符号（ \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e），但是这将会导致证明不出变式一。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但也比在知乎出洋相要好得多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e感谢 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/6808bf0f275d42432d961d5285dc282f\" data-hash=\"6808bf0f275d42432d961d5285dc282f\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$6808bf0f275d42432d961d5285dc282f\"\u003e@Richard Xu\u003c/a\u003e 指正，没有修改原答案的习惯，就把订正写在下面吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在这个命题中 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1%5Cnotin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E%7B-%7D\" alt=\"-1\\notin\\mathbb{P}^{-}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 必然为假。若要证明此命题为真，需要证明“若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e”的部分（记为 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ）亦为假才能证明其为真。而这位高中生误以为说明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 即可证明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为假。而实际上 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p%3Dp_2%5Cvee%7Bp_4%7D%5Cvee%7Bp_6%7D%5Cvee%5Ccdots%2Cp_i%3Ai%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"p=p_2\\vee{p_4}\\vee{p_6}\\vee\\cdots,p_i:i\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，因此说明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 并不能证明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为假。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e原文章被删了，对证明原文感兴趣的知友们可以移步\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53752944\" class=\"internal\"\u003e“证明”存档\u003c/a\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"负质数什么的可以无视它……就权当新提出了一个概念。重点来了：其逆否命题为：若 \\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A} ，则 -1 不是一个质数。 当 n_0=1 时，若 2\\notin{A} ，则 -1 不是一个质数。 这是一个真命题，所以该存在命题为真命题。在假定…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=2\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=0\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":489}}
